<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="158">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$proix" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/proix" class="zg-link" title="不爱说话">不爱说话</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhao-xiao-wen-47-9" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhao-xiao-wen-47-9" class="zg-link" title="赵小文">赵小文</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yao-qing-shu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yao-qing-shu" class="zg-link" title="坠吼是窝">坠吼是窝</a></span>
