<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3611261" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">这个效果叫Low Poly，其数学原理非常简单，就是划分三角形网格，然后用网格中心的颜色填充整个网格。<br><br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/ee6071b88cb8873b5f3264d7c55b0c7d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="810" data-rawheight="518" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="810" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/ee6071b88cb8873b5f3264d7c55b0c7d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="810" data-rawheight="518" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="810" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/ee6071b88cb8873b5f3264d7c55b0c7d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/ee6071b88cb8873b5f3264d7c55b0c7d_b.jpg"><br><br>像这种容易猜出数学表达的效果，一般都有在线工具。<br><br>比如GitHub上的这个：<a href="http://snorpey.github.io/triangulation/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">image triangulation experiment<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/e89dbfaf11cf597a33a5017f520ed172_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1366" data-rawheight="642" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1366" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/e89dbfaf11cf597a33a5017f520ed172_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1366" data-rawheight="642" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1366" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/e89dbfaf11cf597a33a5017f520ed172_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/e89dbfaf11cf597a33a5017f520ed172_b.jpg">


</div>

